[SIZE=6][B]Lib3DObjects[/B][/SIZE]

A library for [B]The Elder Scrolls Online (ESO)[/B] that helps addons create and manipulate [B]3D objects[/B] in the game world.
The goal is a small, easy to use API with lots of room for customization (appearance, transforms, behavior, etc.).

[INDENT][I]Note:[/I] This library is under active development. Expect changes.[/INDENT]

